Fast downloads for daysWi-Fi 6 + 5G ready
FEATURE FILM
We gave the OnePlus Nord 2 a shot of performance-enhancing technology and added a 50 MP AI triple camera system with a Sony IMX766 sensor, optical image stabilization (OIS), and a ton of AI wizardry. Are you ready for next-level shooting?
Caution: Product contains genetically modified camera.
Don’t tell anyone, but we cloned Nord 2’s 50 MP main camera from the ultra wide on the OnePlus 9. More pixels mean higher resolutions, better zoom, and intricate detail.
We’ve finally come to our sensors.
Calling the Sony IMX766 a sensor is a bit misleading. It’s more like a vacuum that sucks up 56% more light for colorful images, extra sharpness, and smooth low-light shooting. And it’s at the core of Nord 2’s main camera.
More you.
And your friends too.
Try some Group Shot 2.0 selfies with the 32 MP front camera. The camera detects and optimizes up to 5 faces for selfies that are a bit less self-centered.
Set a course for fast charging. Maximum Warp!
One of our fastest chargers ever. Warp Charge 65⁵ rockets Nord 2’s 4500mAh³ battery up to a day’s power in just 15 minutes.¹

Nord 2 is powered by MediaTek’s fastest and most powerful chip ever, the MediaTek Dimensity 1200-AI.
It’s an instant upgrade to pretty much everything. Shoot clearer, higher-quality photos and videos. Game faster. Maybe even win more. Stream more cinema-like experiences. The possibilities are limitless.
